{
  "articleContent": "<div>\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">\"The sky's colors melt into the sea. Splashing waves sparkle in the brilliant summer sun. A bird glides across the boundless blue overhead. A slice of watermelon and a perfectly chilled peach parfait. Just another slow summer day for her.\"</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">Chisa's Deluxe Outfit \"Peach Parfait\" will become available once Version 3.5 goes live. Get a sneak peek now!</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"3\" data-line=\"true\">✦How to Obtain✦</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"4\" data-line=\"true\">Chisa's Deluxe Outfit \"Peach Parfait\" will be permanently available in the Store once Version 3.5 goes live.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\">Purchase the Outfit during Version 3.5 at a discount price of 1,980 Lunites. After Version 3.5 ends, the price will return to 2,480 Lunites.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782921600000/ao51jlrb7ku55ge1pw-1782957482091.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782921600000/6dc6rrd4sphpx6fiuo-1782957519959.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782921600000/v4y4vyzkfz9a7mi89n-1782957610789.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782921600000/0ti1vkbm8ghsymdjx1-1782957640285.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782921600000/s7h05cxsc1icgi1o9u-1782957657479.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782921600000/5wf6agcse8easa74lr-1782957674689.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1422\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"5\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
